Invocation Name: lincoln center
des:
The Lincoln Center Alexa skill is updated daily with the performance schedule for Chamber Music Society of Lincoln Center, Film Society of Lincoln Center, Jazz at Lincoln Center, Lincoln Center for the Performing Arts, Lincoln Center Theater, New York City Ballet, New York Philharmonic, New York Public Library for the Performing Arts, The Juilliard School, The Metropolitan Opera, The School of American Ballet. Plan your next trip to New York City by finding out what shows are available on the dates you’re visiting, getting more information about the shows you’re interested in, and getting directions to our venues.

For more information, please visit lincolncenter.org/alexa.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
